### ==================== NOTIFICATIONS ====================
###############################################################################

### 1. List Notifications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications?page=1&page_size=10&unread=true
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 2. Get Notification Detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/<ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 3. Mark Notification as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/<ID>/read
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 4. Mark All Notifications as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 5. Delete Notification
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/<ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

